<div class="saas-agreement">
  <h1>Indemn Services Agreement</h1>

  <h2>1. The Service</h2>
  <p>Indemn ("Company") provides a proprietary Digital Workforce AI platform. Specific deliverables, pricing, and timelines are detailed in the attached Proposal/Order Form, which is incorporated into this agreement.</p>

  <h2>2. Ownership &amp; Data</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><span class="clause-label">Company IP:</span> Indemn owns the platform, AI models, and underlying algorithms.</li>
    <li><span class="clause-label">Customer Data:</span> You own all data you upload. You grant us a license to use it strictly to provide the service.</li>
    <li><span class="clause-label">Anonymized Insights:</span> We may use de-identified, aggregated data to improve our AI models, provided neither you nor your users can be identified.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. The "Safety Net" (AI Oversight)</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><span class="clause-label">Collaborative Tool:</span> The service is designed to assist, not replace, human judgment.</li>
    <li><span class="clause-label">Human-in-the-Loop:</span> High-risk or ambiguous tasks require human review.</li>
    <li><span class="clause-label">Final Authority:</span> The Customer retains sole responsibility for all final underwriting, policy binding, and coverage advice. Indemn is not an insurance carrier or broker.</li>
    <li><span class="clause-label">Review Requirement:</span> You must review AI recommendations flagged for "Human Review". Indemn is not liable for errors resulting from a failure to perform these reviews.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>4. Fees &amp; Payment</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><span class="clause-label">Terms:</span> Fees are defined in the Proposal. Invoices are due Net-30.</li>
    <li><span class="clause-label">Taxes:</span> Customer is responsible for all applicable sales or use taxes.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>5. Performance &amp; Support (SLA)</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><span class="clause-label">Uptime Target:</span> We target 98.9% monthly uptime.</li>
    <li><span class="clause-label">Service Credits:</span> If uptime falls below 98.9%, you are eligible for a credit of 5% of monthly fees for every 1% below the target (capped at 50%).</li>
    <li><span class="clause-label">No AI Warranty:</span> While we warrant the software performs as documented, we do not guarantee that AI-generated output will be 100% error-free.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>6. Liability &amp; Protection</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><span class="clause-label">Mutual Indemnity:</span> We protect you against IP infringement claims regarding our software. You protect us against claims arising from your data or your violation of insurance regulations.</li>
    <li><span class="clause-label">Liability Cap:</span> Total liability for direct damages is capped at the fees paid in the 12 months preceding a claim. Neither party is liable for indirect or consequential damages.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>7. Term &amp; Cancellation</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><span class="clause-label">Termination for Convenience:</span> Either party may cancel this agreement for any reason with 60 days' written notice.</li>
    <li><span class="clause-label">Data Export:</span> Upon termination, you have 7 days to export your data before it is destroyed.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>8. General</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><span class="clause-label">Governing Law:</span> This agreement is governed by the laws of New York.</li>
    <li><span class="clause-label">Publicity:</span> We may use your name in marketing only with your prior written consent.</li>
  </ul>
</div>
